  ],
  "acceptance": [
    "`ATM_LANE_SESSION_ID` resolves by option, env, then lazy mint.",
    "Lazy mint emits `ATM_LANE_SESSION_MINTED` and an export hint.",
    "Same-handle active lanes emit `ATM_LANE_SESSION_ADOPTABLE` with copyable adopt guidance, but bare flows are not blocked.",
    "Missing or closed env lanes emit `ATM_LANE_SESSION_STALE_ENV` and mint a new lane.",
    "Standard CLI JSON can include `laneSession: { laneSessionId, status, source, exportHint }`.",
    "`atm lane status --json` works through the frozen entrypoint.",
    "`cli-result-contract` is updated only if the optional envelope key is locked."
  ],
